Lorenz Attractor HW2

Sean Masucci
CSCI4229/5229 Fall 2021


Provides a visualization of the Lorenz attractor and allows the user to change some of the parameters to manipulate how it looks.


Key bindings
  1      Changes mode to allow the sigma parameter to be changed
  2      Changes mode to allow the beta parameter to be changed
  3      Changes mode to allow the rho parameter to be changed
  +/-    Increase/decrease depending on parameter selected
  arrows Change view angle
  0      Reset view angle and parameters
  ESC    Exit
